  "texts": [
    "AEs also excel in noise reduction, eliminating unwanted artifacts from images, which is pivotal for accurate segmentation (Tripathi 2021).",
    "They are integral in semantic segmentation (Ohgushi et al. 2020), where they classify each pixel in an image, and instance segmentation (Lin et al. 2020), distinguishing individual object instances.",
    "Furthermore, AEs contribute to medical image segmentation (Ma et al. 2022), aiding in the precise identification of structures and anomalies in healthcare images.",
    "Overall, AEs substantially elevate the accuracy and efficiency of image segmentation tasks, encompassing a range of applications that extend from object recognition to medical diagnosis.",
    "AEs find significant applications in the domain of image inpainting, a process of reconstructing missing or corrupted parts of an image."
